      "content": "it's not like the doctors can actually fix it. they just give me pills that make me groggy but the fire is still there. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to end. sometimes i think the only real peace would be if i just... stopped being. if there was just nothingness instead of all this noise. is that a horrible thing to think?",
